{"tid":378631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"薛家燕創立品牌「家燕媽媽」開舖賣手信","createTime":"2017-08-28T15:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T11:59:37.000Z","uid":14730,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e03b87170e9b5f4e09c6242ad2f9a07339d63cf","tid":378631,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/234811_536f0dfc1d18a0f5bbf9984c8baf49bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F234811_536f0dfc1d18a0f5bbf9984c8baf49bd.jpg&h=0f542252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向來有生意頭腦的家燕姐，八十年代已投資錄影帶生意，〇三年又成功塑造「家燕媽媽」形象，創立「家燕媽媽藝術中心」開發新事業。商業頭腦靈活的家燕姐計劃多多，打算再下一城，推出個人品牌打造香港地道食品，希望成為遊客必買的手信，家燕姐說大家對「家燕媽媽」這個名字有親切感，在香港英文註冊名字是Mother Hong Kong，「希望這個品牌可在聖誕前成立，因為這些節日最多人送禮，我亦會用卡通版家燕媽媽來製造曲奇，客人看見我的樣子就已經會笑，會開心，絕對是一個好兆頭，暫時香港會開一間門市和在不同的熱點擺賣。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xGlF5H\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xGlF5H&d=vrvNy2gjRgY9UBp19C%2B5Fy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=48fa458f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xGlF5H</a>"},{"pid":"0ab1c95f9338f528347c4fc15bc909d24c35642c","tid":378631,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a186c6678dda543d5f6671d05f1e32656f44707a","tid":378631,"uid":13919,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/235350_84e679f4c06ec9c7007b2d48ecb8278d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F235350_84e679f4c06ec9c7007b2d48ecb8278d.jpg&h=ce27da36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8f3240ed6775639dcc704028cfe1adbdc3a9b04","tid":378631,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"Mother Hong Kong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f809394de802ee655115d00aeea60c9f87efcb1","tid":378631,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"香港老母 好溫馨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1556cb630c6591eb55a0e8227055e99cac21a4","tid":378631,"uid":42379,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T18:03:29.000Z","msg":"點睇都係盧覓雪加粒墨多過似家燕老母喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766e96376d34a7711731123d1b3497c02bd7963d","tid":378631,"uid":134746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8e57aa1a077b767ce028e30312623da07668dfd","tid":378631,"uid":51051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"會窮"},{"pid":"8a1577602b2b8c675bb0d859d3602986b64dce6f","tid":378631,"uid":107860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T18:53:46.000Z","msg":"早幾年經過星光大道啲souvenir shop見過有桶遮(印象中係粉紅色既) 然後吊住牌子個牌仔寫住&ldquo;家燕遮&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時有cap低圖但好似之後手機虧左冇左張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58985ac5e9ea8225b7fbf2e480538f31c42cd863","tid":378631,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"家燕媽媽 家燕媽媽 家燕媽媽 我的可愛媽媽呵"},{"pid":"6e45de2a65f0dbb9b54eb3efe0358a685b719f9b","tid":378631,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:12:01.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"6ae7b34c1914c18afad2b4af34334179faf2ebb8","tid":378631,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:12:48.000Z","msg":"慈母"},{"pi